631
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:07,040
No. It was the other way around.

632
00:31:09,310 --> 00:31:11,400
She’s outrageous!

633
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:12,230
Master,

634
00:31:12,520 --> 00:31:13,640
leave this to me,

635
00:31:13,830 --> 00:31:15,000
