663
00:33:02,590 --> 00:33:03,800
Master Shangguan.

664
00:33:05,040 --> 00:33:06,000
That’s not true.

665
00:33:09,040 --> 00:33:09,840
Young Master,

666
00:33:10,590 --> 00:33:12,320
