667
00:33:12,470 --> 00:33:13,800
with the manual

668
00:33:13,800 --> 00:33:15,710
when he came by?

669
00:33:16,470 --> 00:33:17,000
Darn!

670
00:33:17,400 --> 00:33:18,280
I was too busy quarreling with him

671
00:33:18,280 --> 00:33:19,340
