673
00:33:24,560 --> 00:33:26,000
Is Miss Chong here?

674
00:33:35,340 --> 00:33:36,980
To Miss Chong

675
00:33:35,430 --> 00:33:36,230
Young Master!

676
00:33:44,430 --> 00:33:46,430
